NekoDTD Readme
==============

Building
--------

You can build NekoDTD with the supplied build.bat file by
typing the following:

  > build -f build-dtd.xml (target ...)

The default target will build the entire package.

To build NekoDTD, you need Ant, Xerces2, and Xalan. The first
time you try to build, it will tell you is required and where
to download the necessary packages.

Documentation
-------------

The documentation for NekoDTD is located at the following URL:

  doc/dtd/index.html

